CONGRATULATIONS!  You have found one of our fantastic Learning Communities.  PSY 102 63U and ENG 122 63U are Learning Communities, meaning that two classes are paired, and students take the two classes together. Assignments in the classes are integrated and coordinated to help students learn class material.  In order to enroll in a learning community, you must register for both classes at the same time.
